INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (1, 1, '皇帝的新装', '许多年以前有一位皇帝，他非常喜欢穿好看的新衣服。他为了要穿得漂亮，把所有的钱都花到衣服上去了，他一点也不关心他的军队，也不喜欢去看戏。除非是为了炫耀一下新衣服，他也不喜欢乘着马车逛公园。他每天每个钟头要换一套新衣服。人们提到皇帝时总是说：“皇上在会议室里。”但是人们一提到他时，总是说：“皇上在更衣室里。”在他住的那个大城市里，生活很轻松，很愉快。每天有许多外国人到来。有一天来了两个骗子。他们说他们是织工。他们说，他们能织出谁也想象不到的最美丽的布。这种布的色彩和图案不仅是非常好看，而且用它缝出来的衣服还有一种奇异的作用，那就是凡是不称职的人或者愚蠢的人，都看不见这衣服。“那正是我最喜欢的衣服！”皇帝心里想。“我穿了这样的衣服，就可以看出我的王国里哪些人不称职；我就可以辨别出哪些人是聪明人，哪些人是傻子。是的，我要叫他们马上织出这样的布来！”他付了许多现款给这两个骗子，叫他们马上开始工作。他们摆出两架织机来，装做是在工作的样子，可是他们的织机上什么东西也没有。他们接二连三地请求皇帝发一些最好的生丝和金子给他们。他们把这些东西都装进自己的腰包，却假装在那两架空空的织机上忙碌地工作，一直忙到深夜。“我很想知道他们织布究竟织得怎样了，”皇帝想。不过，他立刻就想起了愚蠢的人或不称职的人是看不见这布的。他心里的确感到有些不大自在。他相信他自己是用不着害怕的。虽然如此，他还是觉得先派一个人去看看比较妥当。全城的人都听说过这种布料有一种奇异的力量，所以大家都很想趁这机会来测验一下，看看他们的邻人究竟有多笨，有多傻。“我要派诚实的老部长到织工那儿去看看，”皇帝想。“只有他能看出这布料是个什么样子，因为他这个人很有头脑，而且谁也不像他那样称职。”因此这位善良的老部长就到那两个骗子的工作地点去。他们正在空空的织机上忙忙碌碌地工作着。“这是怎么一回事儿？”老部长想，把眼睛睁得有碗口那么大。“我什么东西也没有看见！”但是他不敢把这句话说出来。那两个骗子请求他走近一点，同时问他，布的花纹是不是很美丽，色彩是不是很漂亮。他们指着那两架空空的织机。这位可怜的老大臣的眼睛越睁越大，可是他还是看不见什么东西，因为的确没有什么东西可看。“我的老天爷！”他想。“难道我是一个愚蠢的人吗？我从来没有怀疑过我自己。我决不能让人知道这件事。难道我不称职吗？——不成；我决不能让人知道我看不见布料。”“哎，您一点意见也没有吗？”一个正在织布的织工说。“啊，美极了！真是美妙极了！”老大臣说。他戴着眼镜仔细地看。“多么美的花纹！多么美的色彩！是的，我将要呈报皇上说我对于这布感到非常满意。”“嗯，我们听到您的话真高兴，”两个织工一起说。他们把这些稀有的色彩和花纹描述了一番，还加上些名词儿。这位老大臣注意地听着，以便回到皇帝那里去时，可以照样背得出来。事实上他也就这样办了。这两个骗子又要了很多的钱，更多的丝和金子，他们说这是为了织布的需要。他们把这些东西全装进腰包里，连一根线也没有放到织机上去。不过他们还是继续在空空的机架上工作。过了不久，皇帝派了另一位诚实的官员去看看，布是不是很快就可以织好。他的运气并不比头一位大臣的好：他看了又看，但是那两架空空的织机上什么也没有，他什么东西也看不出来。“您看这段布美不美？”两个骗子问。他们指着一些美丽的花纹，并且作了一些解释。事实上什么花纹也没有。“我并不愚蠢！”这位官员想。“这大概是因为我不配担当现在这样好的官职吧？这也真够滑稽，但是我决不能让人看出来！”因此他就把他完全没有看见的布称赞了一番，同时对他们说，他非常喜欢这些美丽的颜色和巧妙的花纹。“是的，那真是太美了，”他回去对皇帝说。城里所有的人都在谈论这美丽的布料。当这布还在织的时候，皇帝就很想亲自去看一次。他选了一群特别圈定的随员——其中包括已经去看过的那两位诚实的大臣。这样，他就到那两个狡猾的骗子住的地方去。这两个家伙正以全副精神织布，但是一根线的影子也看不见。“您看这不漂亮吗？”那两位诚实的官员说。“陛下请看，多么美丽的花纹！多么美丽的色彩！”他们指着那架空空的织机，因为他们以为别人一定会看得见布料的。“这是怎么一回事儿呢？”皇帝心里想。“我什么也没有看见！这真是荒唐！难道我是一个愚蠢的人吗？难道我不配做皇帝吗？这真是我从来没有碰见过的一件最可怕的事情。”“啊，它真是美极了！”皇帝说。“我表示十二分地满意！”于是他点头表示满意。他装做很仔细地看着织机的样子，因为他不愿意说出他什么也没有看见。跟他来的全体随员也仔细地看了又看，可是他们也没有看出更多的东西。不过，他们也照着皇帝的话说：“啊，真是美极了！”他们建议皇帝用这种新奇的、美丽的布料做成衣服，穿上这衣服亲自去参加快要举行的游行大典。“真美丽！真精致！真是好极了！”每人都随声附和着。每人都有说不出的快乐。皇帝赐给骗子每人一个爵士的头衔和一枚可以挂在纽扣洞上的勋章；并且还封他们为“御聘织师”。第二天早晨游行大典就要举行了。在头天晚上，这两个骗子整夜不睡，点起１６支蜡烛。你可以看到他们是在赶夜工，要完成皇帝的新衣。他们装做把布料从织机上取下来。他们用两把大剪刀在空中裁了一阵子，同时又用没有穿线的针缝了一通。最后，他们齐声说：“请看！新衣服缝好了！”皇帝带着他的一群最高贵的骑士们亲自到来了。这两个骗子每人举起一只手，好像他们拿着一件什么东西似的。他们说：“请看吧，这是裤子，这是袍子！这是外衣！”等等。“这衣服轻柔得像蜘蛛网一样：穿着它的人会觉得好像身上没有什么东西似的——这也正是这衣服的妙处。”“一点也不错，”所有的骑士们都说。可是他们什么也没有看见，因为实际上什么东西也没有。“现在请皇上脱下衣服，”两个骗子说，“我们要在这个大镜子面前为陛下换上新衣。皇帝把身上的衣服统统都脱光了。这两个骗子装做把他们刚才缝好的新衣服一件一件地交给他。他们在他的腰围那儿弄了一阵子，好像是系上一件什么东西似的：这就是后裾就是拖在礼服后面的很长的一块布；它是封建时代欧洲贵族的一种装束。）。皇帝在镜子面前转了转身子，扭了扭腰肢。“上帝，这衣服多么合身啊！式样裁得多么好看啊！”大家都说。“多么美的花纹！多么美的色彩！这真是一套贵重的衣服！”“大家已经在外面把华盖准备好了，只等陛下一出去，就可撑起来去游行！”典礼官说。“对，我已经穿好了，”皇帝说，“这衣服合我的身么？”于是他又在镜子面前把身子转动了一下，因为他要叫大家看出他在认真地欣赏他美丽的服装。那些将要托着后裾的内臣们，都把手在地上东摸西摸，好像他们真的在拾其后裾似的。他们开步走，手中托着空气——他们不敢让人瞧出他们实在什么东西也没有看见。这么着，皇帝就在那个富丽的华盖下游行起来了。站在街上和窗子里的人都说：“乖乖，皇上的新装真是漂亮！他上衣下面的后裾是多么美丽！衣服多么合身！”谁也不愿意让人知道自己看不见什么东西，因为这样就会暴露自己不称职，或是太愚蠢。皇帝所有的衣服从来没有得到这样普遍的称赞。“可是他什么衣服也没有穿呀！”一个小孩子最后叫出声来。“上帝哟，你听这个天真的声音！”爸爸说。于是大家把这孩子讲的话私自低声地传播开来。“他并没有穿什么衣服！有一个小孩子说他并没有穿什么衣服呀！”“他实在是没有穿什么衣服呀！”最后所有的老百姓都说。皇帝有点儿发抖，因为他似乎觉得老百姓所讲的话是对的。不过他自己心里却这样想：“我必须把这游行大典举行完毕。”因此他摆出一副更骄傲的神气，他的内臣们跟在他后面走，手中托着一个并不存在的后裾。', 1, '2025-10-20 22:04:35', '2025-10-22 15:01:07', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (2, 1, '皇帝的新装', '许多年以前有一位皇帝，他非常喜欢穿好看的新衣服。他为了要穿得漂亮，把所有的钱都花到衣服上去了，他一点也不关心他的军队，也不喜欢去看戏。除非是为了炫耀一下新衣服，他也不喜欢乘着马车逛公园。他每天每个钟头要换一套新衣服。人们提到皇帝时总是说：“皇上在会议室里。”但是人们一提到他时，总是说：“皇上在更衣室里。”\r\n\r\n在他住的那个大城市里，生活很轻松，很愉快。每天有许多外国人到来。有一天来了两个骗子。他们说他们是织工。他们说，他们能织出谁也想象不到的最美丽的布。这种布的色彩和图案不仅是非常好看，而且用它缝出来的衣服还有一种奇异的作用，那就是凡是不称职的人或者愚蠢的人，都看不见这衣服。\r\n\r\n“那正是我最喜欢的衣服！”皇帝心里想。“我穿了这样的衣服，就可以看出我的王国里哪些人不称职；我就可以辨别出哪些人是聪明人，哪些人是傻子。是的，我要叫他们马上织出这样的布来！”他付了许多现款给这两个骗子，叫他们马上开始工作。\r\n\r\n他们摆出两架织机来，装做是在工作的样子，可是他们的织机上什么东西也没有。他们接二连三地请求皇帝发一些最好的生丝和金子给他们。他们把这些东西都装进自己的腰包，却假装在那两架空空的织机上忙碌地工作，一直忙到深夜。\r\n\r\n“我很想知道他们织布究竟织得怎样了，”皇帝想。不过，他立刻就想起了愚蠢的人或不称职的人是看不见这布的。他心里的确感到有些不大自在。他相信他自己是用不着害怕的。虽然如此，他还是觉得先派一个人去看看比较妥当。全城的人都听说过这种布料有一种奇异的力量，所以大家都很想趁这机会来测验一下，看看他们的邻人究竟有多笨，有多傻。\r\n\r\n“我要派诚实的老部长到织工那儿去看看，”皇帝想。“只有他能看出这布料是个什么样子，因为他这个人很有头脑，而且谁也不像他那样称职。”\r\n\r\n因此这位善良的老部长就到那两个骗子的工作地点去。他们正在空空的织机上忙忙碌碌地工作着。\r\n\r\n“这是怎么一回事儿？”老部长想，把眼睛睁得有碗口那么大。\r\n\r\n“我什么东西也没有看见！”但是他不敢把这句话说出来。\r\n\r\n那两个骗子请求他走近一点，同时问他，布的花纹是不是很美丽，色彩是不是很漂亮。他们指着那两架空空的织机。\r\n\r\n这位可怜的老大臣的眼睛越睁越大，可是他还是看不见什么东西，因为的确没有什么东西可看。\r\n\r\n“我的老天爷！”他想。“难道我是一个愚蠢的人吗？我从来没有怀疑过我自己。我决不能让人知道这件事。难道我不称职吗？——不成；我决不能让人知道我看不见布料。”\r\n\r\n“哎，您一点意见也没有吗？”一个正在织布的织工说。\r\n\r\n“啊，美极了！真是美妙极了！”老大臣说。他戴着眼镜仔细地看。“多么美的花纹！多么美的色彩！是的，我将要呈报皇上说我对于这布感到非常满意。”\r\n\r\n“嗯，我们听到您的话真高兴，”两个织工一起说。他们把这些稀有的色彩和花纹描述了一番，还加上些名词儿。这位老大臣注意地听着，以便回到皇帝那里去时，可以照样背得出来。事实上他也就这样办了。\r\n\r\n这两个骗子又要了很多的钱，更多的丝和金子，他们说这是为了织布的需要。他们把这些东西全装进腰包里，连一根线也没有放到织机上去。不过他们还是继续在空空的机架上工作。\r\n\r\n过了不久，皇帝派了另一位诚实的官员去看看，布是不是很快就可以织好。他的运气并不比头一位大臣的好：他看了又看，但是那两架空空的织机上什么也没有，他什么东西也看不出来。\r\n\r\n“您看这段布美不美？”两个骗子问。他们指着一些美丽的花纹，并且作了一些解释。事实上什么花纹也没有。\r\n\r\n“我并不愚蠢！”这位官员想。“这大概是因为我不配担当现在这样好的官职吧？这也真够滑稽，但是我决不能让人看出来！”因此他就把他完全没有看见的布称赞了一番，同时对他们说，他非常喜欢这些美丽的颜色和巧妙的花纹。“是的，那真是太美了，”他回去对皇帝说。\r\n\r\n城里所有的人都在谈论这美丽的布料。\r\n\r\n当这布还在织的时候，皇帝就很想亲自去看一次。他选了一群特别圈定的随员——其中包括已经去看过的那两位诚实的大臣。这样，他就到那两个狡猾的骗子住的地方去。这两个家伙正以全副精神织布，但是一根线的影子也看不见。“您看这不漂亮吗？”那两位诚实的官员说。“陛下请看，多么美丽的花纹！多么美丽的色彩！”他们指着那架空空的织机，因为他们以为别人一定会看得见布料的。\r\n\r\n“这是怎么一回事儿呢？”皇帝心里想。“我什么也没有看见！这真是荒唐！难道我是一个愚蠢的人吗？难道我不配做皇帝吗？这真是我从来没有碰见过的一件最可怕的事情。”\r\n\r\n“啊，它真是美极了！”皇帝说。“我表示十二分地满意！”\r\n\r\n于是他点头表示满意。他装做很仔细地看着织机的样子，因为他不愿意说出他什么也没有看见。跟他来的全体随员也仔细地看了又看，可是他们也没有看出更多的东西。不过，他们也照着皇帝的话说：“啊，真是美极了！”他们建议皇帝用这种新奇的、美丽的布料做成衣服，穿上这衣服亲自去参加快要举行的游行大典。“真美丽！真精致！真是好极了！”每人都随声附和着。每人都有说不出的快乐。皇帝赐给骗子每人一个爵士的头衔和一枚可以挂在纽扣洞上的勋章；并且还封他们为“御聘织师”。\r\n\r\n第二天早晨游行大典就要举行了。在头天晚上，这两个骗子整夜不睡，点起１６支蜡烛。你可以看到他们是在赶夜工，要完成皇帝的新衣。他们装做把布料从织机上取下来。他们用两把大剪刀在空中裁了一阵子，同时又用没有穿线的针缝了一通。最后，他们齐声说：“请看！新衣服缝好了！”\r\n\r\n皇帝带着他的一群最高贵的骑士们亲自到来了。这两个骗子每人举起一只手，好像他们拿着一件什么东西似的。他们说：“请看吧，这是裤子，这是袍子！这是外衣！”等等。“这衣服轻柔得像蜘蛛网一样：穿着它的人会觉得好像身上没有什么东西似的——这也正是这衣服的妙处。”\r\n\r\n“一点也不错，”所有的骑士们都说。可是他们什么也没有看见，因为实际上什么东西也没有。\r\n\r\n“现在请皇上脱下衣服，”两个骗子说，“我们要在这个大镜子面前为陛下换上新衣。\r\n\r\n皇帝把身上的衣服统统都脱光了。这两个骗子装做把他们刚才缝好的新衣服一件一件地交给他。他们在他的腰围那儿弄了一阵子，好像是系上一件什么东西似的：这就是后裾就是拖在礼服后面的很长的一块布；它是封建时代欧洲贵族的一种装束。）。皇帝在镜子面前转了转身子，扭了扭腰肢。\r\n\r\n“上帝，这衣服多么合身啊！式样裁得多么好看啊！”大家都说。“多么美的花纹！多么美的色彩！这真是一套贵重的衣服！”\r\n\r\n“大家已经在外面把华盖准备好了，只等陛下一出去，就可撑起来去游行！”典礼官说。\r\n\r\n“对，我已经穿好了，”皇帝说，“这衣服合我的身么？”于是他又在镜子面前把身子转动了一下，因为他要叫大家看出他在认真地欣赏他美丽的服装。那些将要托着后裾的内臣们，都把手在地上东摸西摸，好像他们真的在拾其后裾似的。他们开步走，手中托着空气——他们不敢让人瞧出他们实在什么东西也没有看见。\r\n\r\n这么着，皇帝就在那个富丽的华盖下游行起来了。站在街上和窗子里的人都说：“乖乖，皇上的新装真是漂亮！他上衣下面的后裾是多么美丽！衣服多么合身！”谁也不愿意让人知道自己看不见什么东西，因为这样就会暴露自己不称职，或是太愚蠢。皇帝所有的衣服从来没有得到这样普遍的称赞。\r\n\r\n“可是他什么衣服也没有穿呀！”一个小孩子最后叫出声来。\r\n\r\n“上帝哟，你听这个天真的声音！”爸爸说。于是大家把这孩子讲的话私自低声地传播开来。\r\n\r\n“他并没有穿什么衣服！有一个小孩子说他并没有穿什么衣服呀！”\r\n\r\n“他实在是没有穿什么衣服呀！”最后所有的老百姓都说。\r\n\r\n皇帝有点儿发抖，因为他似乎觉得老百姓所讲的话是对的。不过他自己心里却这样想：“我必须把这游行大典举行完毕。”因此他摆出一副更骄傲的神气，他的内臣们跟在他后面走，手中托着一个并不存在的后裾。', 2, '2025-10-22 19:08:41', '2025-10-22 19:08:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (3, 1, '皇帝的新装', '许多年以前有一位皇帝，他非常喜欢穿好看的新衣服。他为了要穿得漂亮，把所有的钱都花到衣服上去了，他一点也不关心他的军队，也不喜欢去看戏。', 3, '2025-10-25 11:20:53', '2025-10-25 11:20:53', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (4, 2, '卖火柴的小女孩', '天气冷得可怕。正在下雪，黑暗的夜幕开始垂下来了。这是这年最后的一夜——新年的前夕。在这样的寒冷和黑暗中，有一个光头赤脚的小女孩正在街上走着。是的，她离开家的时候还穿着一双拖鞋，但那又有什么用呢？那是一双非常大的拖鞋——那么大，最近她妈妈一直在穿着。当她匆忙地越过街道的时候，两辆马车飞奔着闯过来，弄得这小姑娘把鞋跑落了。有一只她怎样也寻不到，另一只又被一个男孩子捡起来，拿着逃走了。这男孩子还说，等他自己将来有孩子的时候，可以把它当作一个摇篮来使用。现在这小姑娘只好赤着一双小脚走。小脚已经冻得发红发青了。她有许多火柴包在一个旧围裙里；她手中还拿着一扎。这一整天谁也没有向她买过一根；谁也没有给她一个铜板。可怜的小姑娘！她又饿又冻地向前走，简直是一幅愁苦的画面。雪花落到她金黄的长头发上——它卷曲地铺散在她的肩上，看起来非常美丽。不过她并没有想到自己的漂亮。所有的窗子都射出光来，街上飘着一股烤鹅肉¹的香味。的确，这是除夕。她在想这件事情。那儿有两座房子，其中一座房子比另一座更向街心伸出一点，她便在这个墙角里坐下来，缩作一团。她把一双小脚也缩进来，不过她感到更冷。她不敢回到家里去，因为她没有卖掉一根火柴，没有赚到一个铜板。她的父亲一定会打她，而且家里也是很冷的，因为他们头上只有一个风可以从那上面灌进来的屋顶，虽然最大的裂口已经用草和破布堵住了。她的一双小手几乎冻僵了。唉！哪怕一根小火柴对她也是有好处的。只要她敢抽出一根来，在墙上擦着了，就可以暖手！最后她抽出一根来了。哧！它燃起来了，冒出火光来了！当她把手覆在上面的时候，小姑娘觉得真像坐在一个铁火炉旁边一样：它有光亮的黄铜圆捏手和黄铜炉身。火烧得那么欢，那么暖，那么美！唉，这是怎么一回事？当小姑娘刚刚伸出一双脚、打算暖一暖脚的时候，火焰就忽然熄灭了！火炉也不见了。她坐在那儿，手中只有烧过了的火柴。她又擦了一根。它燃起来了，发出光来了。墙上有亮光照着的那块地方，现在变得透明，像一片薄纱；她可以看到房间里的东西：桌上铺着雪白的台布，上面有精致的碗盘，填满了梅子和苹果的、冒着香气的烤鹅。更美妙的事情是：这只鹅从盘子里跳出来了，背上插着刀叉，蹒跚地在地上走着，一直向这个穷苦的小姑娘面前走来。这时火柴就熄灭了；她面前只有一堵又厚又冷的墙。她点了另一根火柴。现在她是坐在美丽的圣诞树下面。上次圣诞节时，她透过玻璃门，看到一个富有商人家里的一株圣诞树；可是现在这一株比那株还要大，还要美。它的绿枝上燃着几千支蜡烛；彩色的图画，跟橱窗里挂着的那些一样美丽，在向她眨眼。这个小姑娘把两只手伸过去。于是火柴就灭了。圣诞节的烛光越升越高。她看到它们现在变成了明亮的星星。这些星星有一颗落下来了，在天上划出一条长长的光线。“现在又有一个什么人死去了，”小姑娘说，因为她的老祖母曾经说过：天上落下一颗星，地上就有一个灵魂升到上帝那儿去。¹老祖母是唯一对她好的人，但是现在已经死了。她在墙上又擦了一根火柴。它把四周都照亮了；在这亮光中老祖母出现了。她显得那么光明，那么温柔，那么和蔼。“祖母！”小姑娘叫起来，“啊！请把我带走吧！我知道，这火柴一灭掉，你就会不见了，你就会像那个温暖的火炉，那只美丽的烤鹅，那棵幸福的圣诞树一样地不见了！”于是她急忙把整束火柴中剩下的火柴都擦亮了，因为她非常想把祖母留住。这些火柴发出强烈的光芒，照得比大白天还要明朗。祖母从来没有像现在这样显得美丽和高大。她把小姑娘抱起来，搂到怀里。她们两人在光明和快乐中飞走了，越飞越高，飞到既没有寒冷，也没有饥饿，也没有忧愁的那块地方——她们是跟上帝在一起。不过在一个寒冷的清晨，这个小姑娘却坐在一个墙角里；她的双颊通红，嘴唇发出微笑，她已经死了——在旧年的除夕冻死了。新年的太阳升起来了，照着她小小的尸体！她坐在那儿，手中还捏着火柴——其中有一扎差不多都烧光了。“她想把自己暖和一下。”人们说。谁也不知道：她曾经看到过多么美丽的东西，她曾经是多么光荣地跟祖母一起，走到新年的幸福中去。', 1, '2025-10-27 16:29:22', '2025-10-27 16:29:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (5, 3, '小红帽', '从前有个可爱的小姑娘，谁见了都喜欢，但最喜欢她的是她的奶奶，简直是她要什么就给她什么。 一次，奶奶送给小姑娘一顶用丝绒做的小红帽，戴在她的头上正好合适。 从此，姑娘再也不愿意戴任何别的帽子，于是大家便叫她\"小红帽\"。一天，妈妈对小红帽说：\"来，小红帽，这里有一块蛋糕和一瓶葡萄酒，快给奶奶送去，奶奶生病了，身子很虚弱，吃了这些就会好一些的。趁着现在天还没有热，赶紧动身吧。在路上要好好走，不要跑，也不要离开大路，否则你会摔跤的，那样奶奶就什么也吃不上了。到奶奶家的时候，别忘了说\'早上好\'，也不要一进屋就东瞧西瞅。\"\"我会小心的。\"小红帽对妈妈说，并且还和妈妈拉手作保证。奶奶住在村子外面的森林里，离小红帽家有很长一段路。 小红帽刚走进森林就碰到了一条狼。 小红帽不知道狼是坏家伙，所以一点也不怕它。\"你好，小红帽，\"狼说。\"谢谢你，狼先生。\"\"小红帽，这么早要到哪里去呀？\"\"我要到奶奶家去。\"\"你那围裙下面有什么呀？\"\"蛋糕和葡萄酒。昨天我们家烤了一些蛋糕，可怜的奶奶生了病，要吃一些好东西才能恢复过来。\"\"你奶奶住在哪里呀，小红帽？\"\"进了林子还有一段路呢。她的房子就在三棵大橡树下，低处围着核桃树篱笆。你一定知道的。\"小红帽说。狼在心中盘算着：\"这小东西细皮嫩肉的，味道肯定比那老太婆要好。我要讲究一下策略，让她俩都逃不出我的手心。\"于是它陪着小红帽走了一会儿，然后说：\"小红帽，你看周围这些花多么美丽啊！干吗不回头看一看呢？还有这些小鸟，它们唱得多么动听啊！你大概根本没有听到吧？林子里的一切多么美好啊，而你却只管往前走，就像是去上学一样。\"小红帽抬起头来，看到阳光在树木间来回跳荡，美丽的鲜花在四周开放，便想：\"也许我该摘一把鲜花给奶奶，让她高兴高兴。现在天色还早，我不会去迟的。\"她于是离开大路，走进林子去采花。 她每采下一朵花，总觉得前面还有更美丽的花朵，便又向前走去，结果一直走到了林子深处。就在此时，狼却直接跑到奶奶家，敲了敲门。\"是谁呀？\"\"是小红帽。\"狼回答，\"我给你送蛋糕和葡萄酒来了。快开门哪。\"\"你拉一下门栓就行了，\"奶奶大声说，\"我身上没有力气，起不来。\"狼刚拉起门栓，那门就开了。 狼二话没说就冲到奶奶的床前，把奶奶吞进了肚子。 然后她穿上奶奶的衣服，戴上她的帽子，躺在床上，还拉上了帘子。可这时小红帽还在跑来跑去地采花。 直到采了许多许多，她都拿不了啦，她才想起奶奶，重新上路去奶奶家。看到奶奶家的屋门敞开着，她感到很奇怪。 她一走进屋子就有一种异样的感觉，心中便想：\"天哪！平常我那么喜欢来奶奶家，今天怎么这样害怕？\"她大声叫道：\"早上好！\"，可是没有听到回答。 她走到床前拉开帘子，只见奶奶躺在床上，帽子拉得低低的，把脸都遮住了，样子非常奇怪。\"哎，奶奶，\"她说，\"你的耳朵怎么这样大呀？\"\"为了更好地听你说话呀，乖乖。\"\"可是奶奶，你的眼睛怎么这样大呀？\"小红帽又问。\"为了更清楚地看你呀，乖乖。\"\"奶奶，你的手怎么这样大呀？\"\"可以更好地抱着你呀。\"\"奶奶，你的嘴巴怎么大得很吓人呀？\"\"可以一口把你吃掉呀！\"狼刚把话说完，就从床上跳起来，把小红帽吞进了肚子，狼满足了食欲之后便重新躺到床上睡觉，而且鼾声震天。 一位猎人碰巧从屋前走过，心想：\"这老太太鼾打得好响啊！我要进去看看她是不是出什么事了。\"猎人进了屋，来到床前时却发现躺在那里的竟是狼。 \"你这老坏蛋，我找了你这么久，真没想到在这里找到你！\"他说。 他正准备向狼开枪，突然又想到，这狼很可能把奶奶吞进了肚子，奶奶也许还活着。 猎人就没有开枪，而是操起一把剪刀，动手把呼呼大睡的狼的肚子剪了开来。 他刚剪了两下，就看到了红色的小帽子。 他又剪了两下，小姑娘便跳了出来，叫道：\"真把我吓坏了！狼肚子里黑漆漆的。\"接着，奶奶也活着出来了，只是有点喘不过气来。 小红帽赶紧跑去搬来几块大石头，塞进狼的肚子。 狼醒来之后想逃走，可是那些石头太重了，它刚站起来就跌到在地，摔死了。三个人高兴极了。 猎人剥下狼皮，回家去了；奶奶吃了小红帽带来的蛋糕和葡萄酒，精神好多了；而小红帽却在想：\"要是妈妈不允许，我一辈子也不独自离开大路，跑进森林了。\"人们还说，小红帽后来又有一次把蛋糕送给奶奶，而且在路上又有一只狼跟她搭话，想骗她离开大路。 可小红帽这次提高了警惕，头也不回地向前走。 她告诉奶奶她碰到了狼，那家伙嘴上虽然对她说\"你好\"，眼睛里却露着凶光，要不是在大路上，它准把她给吃了。 \"那么，\"奶奶说，\"我们把门关紧，不让它进来。\"不一会儿，狼真的一面敲着门一面叫道：\"奶奶，快开门呀。我是小红帽，给你送蛋糕来了。\"但是她们既不说话，也不开门。 这长着灰毛的家伙围着房子转了两三圈，最后跳上屋顶，打算等小红帽在傍晚回家时偷偷跟在她的后面，趁天黑把她吃掉。 可奶奶看穿了这家伙的坏心思。 她想起屋子前有一个大石头槽子，便对小姑娘说：\"小红帽，把桶拿来。我昨天做了一些香肠，提些煮香肠的水去倒进石头槽里。\"小红帽提了很多很多水，把那个大石头槽子装得满满的。 香肠的气味飘进了狼的鼻孔，它使劲地用鼻子闻呀闻，并且朝下张望着，到最后把脖子伸得太长了，身子开始往下滑。 它从屋顶上滑了下来，正好落在大石槽中，淹死了。 小红帽高高兴兴地回了家，从此再也没有谁伤害过她。\r\n', 1, '2025-10-28 11:19:19', '2025-10-28 11:19:19', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story` VALUES (6, 4, '小红帽（英文版）', 'Once upon a time there was a sweet little girl. Everyone who saw her liked her, but most of all her grandmother, who did not know what to give the child next. Once she gave her a little cap made of red velvet. Because it suited her so well, and she wanted to wear it all the time, she came to be known as Little Red Riding Hood. One day her mother said to her: \"Come Little Red Riding Hood. Here is a piece of cake and a bottle of wine. Take them to your grandmother. She is sick and weak, and they will do her well. Mind your manners and give her my greetings. Behave yourself on the way, and do not leave the path, or you might fall down and break the glass, and then there will be nothing for your sick grandmother.\"Little Red Riding Hood promised to obey her mother. The grandmother lived out in the woods, a half hour from the village. When Little Red Riding Hood entered the woods a wolf came up to her. She did not know what a wicked animal he was, and was not afraid of him. \"Good day to you, Little Red Riding Hood.\" - \"Thank you, wolf.\" - \"Where are you going so early, Little Red Riding Hood?\" - \"To grandmother\'s.\" - \"And what are you carrying under your apron?\" - \"Grandmother is sick and weak, and I am taking her some cake and wine. We baked yesterday, and they should give her strength.\" - \"Little Red Riding Hood, just where does your grandmother live?\" - \"Her house is a good quarter hour from here in the woods, under the three large oak trees. There\'s a hedge of hazel bushes there. You must know the place,\" said Little Red Riding Hood. The wolf thought to himself: \"Now there is a tasty bite for me. Just how are you going to catch her?\" Then he said: \"Listen, Little Red Riding Hood, haven\'t you seen the beautiful flowers that are blossoming in the woods? Why don\'t you go and take a look? And I don\'t believe you can hear how beautifully the birds are singing. You are walking along as though you were on your way to school in the village. It is very beautiful in the woods.\"Little Red Riding Hood opened her eyes and saw the sunlight breaking through the trees and how the ground was covered with beautiful flowers. She thought: \"If a take a bouquet to grandmother, she will be very pleased. Anyway, it is still early, and I\'ll be home on time.\" And she ran off into the woods looking for flowers. Each time she picked one she thought that she could see an even more beautiful one a little way off, and she ran after it, going further and further into the woods. But the wolf ran straight to the grandmother\'s house and knocked on the door. \"Who\'s there?\" - \"Little Red Riding Hood. I\'m bringing you some cake and wine. Open the door for me.\" - \"Just press the latch,\" called out the grandmother. \"I\'m too weak to get up.\" The wolf pressed the latch, and the door opened. He stepped inside, went straight to the grandmother\'s bed, and ate her up. Then he took her clothes, put them on, and put her cap on his head. He got into her bed and pulled the curtains shut.Little Red Riding Hood had run after flowers, and did not continue on her way to grandmother\'s until she had gathered all that she could carry. When she arrived, she found, to her surprise, that the door was open. She walked into the parlor, and everything looked so strange that she thought: \"Oh, my God, why am I so afraid? I usually like it at grandmother\'s.\" Then she went to the bed and pulled back the curtains. Grandmother was lying there with her cap pulled down over her face and looking very strange. \"Oh, grandmother, what big ears you have!\" - \"All the better to hear you with.\" - \"Oh, grandmother, what big eyes you have!\" - \"All the better to see you with.\" - \"Oh, grandmother, what big hands you have!\" - \"All the better to grab you with!\" - \"Oh, grandmother, what a horribly big mouth you have!\" - \"All the better to eat you with!\" And with that he jumped out of bed, jumped on top of poor Little Red Riding Hood, and ate her up.As soon as the wolf had finished this tasty bite, he climbed back into bed, fell asleep, and began to snore very loudly. A huntsman was just passing by. He thought it strange that the old woman was snoring so loudly, so he decided to take a look. He stepped inside, and in the bed there lay the wolf that he had been hunting for such a long time. \"He has eaten the grandmother, but perhaps she still can be saved. I won\'t shoot him,\" thought the huntsman. So he took a pair of scissors and cut open his belly. He had cut only a few strokes when he saw the red cap shining through. He cut a little more, and the girl jumped out and cried: \"Oh, I was so frightened! It was so dark inside the wolf\'s body!\" And then the grandmother came out alive as well. Then Little Red Riding Hood fetched some large heavy stones. They filled the wolf\'s body with them, and when he woke up and tried to run away, the stones were so heavy that he fell down dead.The three of them were happy. The huntsman took the wolf\'s pelt. The grandmother ate the cake and drank the wine that Little Red Riding Hood had brought. And Little Red Riding Hood thought to herself: \"As long as I live, I will never leave the path and run off into the woods by myself if mother tells me not to.\"', 1, '2025-10-28 11:24:18', '2025-10-28 11:24:18', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (3, 4, '{\"text\": \"天气冷得可怕。正在下雪，黑暗的夜幕开始垂下来了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"文本描述寒冷黑暗的环境，体现忧郁氛围，故调整维度5为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"场景铺垫结束，中等停顿引入时间背景\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 630, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，630 tokens匹配稍慢语速营造压抑感\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 1, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (4, 4, '{\"text\": \"这是这年最后的一夜——新年的前夕。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"时间陈述无明显情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且语义完整，情感中性\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短文本，500 tokens保证节奏平稳\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 2, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (5, 4, '{\"text\": \"在这样的寒冷和黑暗中，有一个光头赤脚的小女孩正在街上走着。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述小女孩赤脚在寒冷中行走，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"引入主角且情绪沉重，稍长停顿增强代入感\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 3, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (6, 4, '{\"text\": \"是的，她离开家的时候还穿着一双拖鞋，但那又有什么用呢？\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"反问句表达无奈，混合悲伤(0.2)与忧郁(0.1)，总和0.3符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"问号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"疑问句结尾，中等停顿保持叙事连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度疑问句，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 4, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (7, 4, '{\"text\": \"那是一双非常大的拖鞋——那么大，最近她妈妈一直在穿着。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述不合脚的拖鞋暗示贫困，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 5, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (8, 4, '{\"text\": \"当她匆忙地越过街道的时候，两辆马车飞奔着闯过来，弄得这小姑娘把鞋跑落了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述突发危险场景，体现害怕情绪，故调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"事件结束且情绪紧张，稍长停顿缓冲\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配稍快语速表现紧张感\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 6, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (9, 4, '{\"text\": \"有一只她怎样也寻不到，另一只又被一个男孩子捡起来，拿着逃走了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述失去鞋子的无助，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"事件结束，中等停顿连接后续描述\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 7, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (10, 4, '{\"text\": \"这男孩子还说，等他自己将来有孩子的时候，可以把它当作一个摇篮来使用。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"转述他人话语无明显情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感中性，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"36字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 8, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (11, 4, '{\"text\": \"现在这小姑娘只好赤着一双小脚走。小脚已经冻得发红发青了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述冻伤的小脚体现痛苦，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"身体痛苦描述结束，稍长停顿增强感染力\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 9, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (12, 4, '{\"text\": \"她有许多火柴包在一个旧围裙里；她手中还拿着一扎。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"客观描述物品状态，无明显情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感中性，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"分号连接的完整句，常规停顿保持流畅\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配平稳语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 10, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (13, 4, '{\"text\": \"这一整天谁也没有向她买过一根；谁也没有给她一个铜板。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"重复强调无人帮助，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"强调孤独无助，稍长停顿增强情感表达\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 11, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (14, 4, '{\"text\": \"可怜的小姑娘！她又饿又冻地向前走，简直是一幅愁苦的画面。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"直接感叹\'可怜\'且描述愁苦，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.2)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感强烈，符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮处，延长停顿强调悲惨处境\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度感叹句，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 12, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (15, 4, '{\"text\": \"雪花落到她金黄的长头发上——它卷曲地铺散在她的肩上，看起来非常美丽。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述外貌美丽但无情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感中性，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"36字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配舒缓语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 13, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (16, 4, '{\"text\": \"不过她并没有想到自己的漂亮。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"暗示忽视自身美丽因处境悲惨，混合悲伤(0.2)与忧郁(0.1)，总和0.3符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"转折句结束，中等停顿连接后续场景\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，500 tokens保证节奏平稳\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 14, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (17, 4, '{\"text\": \"所有的窗子都射出光来，街上飘着一股烤鹅肉的香味。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"环境描写无情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感中性，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配平稳语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 15, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (18, 4, '{\"text\": \"的确，这是除夕。她在想这件事情。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对比节日氛围与自身处境，体现忧郁情绪，故调整维度5为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"心理活动结束，中等停顿连接场景转换\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，550 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 16, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (19, 4, '{\"text\": \"那儿有两座房子，其中一座房子比另一座更向街心伸出一点，她便在这个墙角里坐下来，缩作一团。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述蜷缩动作体现无助，故调整维度5为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"动作结束且情绪压抑，稍长停顿增强画面感\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 17, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (20, 4, '{\"text\": \"她把一双小脚也缩进来，不过她感到更冷。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"直接描述寒冷痛苦，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"身体感受描述结束，中等停顿连接原因说明\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"22字短文本，600 tokens匹配稍快语速表现不适感\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 18, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (21, 4, '{\"text\": \"她不敢回到家里去，因为她没有卖掉一根火柴，没有赚到一个铜板。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0.1, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述恐惧回家混合悲伤，调整维度2(0.2)、3(0.1)、5(0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（混合负面情绪），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"原因说明结束，稍长停顿连接家庭状况\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 19, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (22, 4, '{\"text\": \"她的父亲一定会打她，而且家里也是很冷的，因为他们头上只有一个风可以从那上面灌进来的屋顶，虽然最大的裂口已经用草和破布堵住了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0.1, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述家暴威胁与恶劣居住条件，混合悲伤(0.3)、害怕(0.1)、忧郁(0.1)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（混合负面情绪），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"家庭困境描述结束，延长停顿强调绝望感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 850, \"duration_reason\": \"58字较长文本，850 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 20, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (23, 4, '{\"text\": \"她的一双小手几乎冻僵了。唉！哪怕一根小火柴对她也是有好处的。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述冻僵状态体现痛苦，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"感叹句结束，稍长停顿引出行动\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 21, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (24, 4, '{\"text\": \"只要她敢抽出一根来，在墙上擦着了，就可以暖手！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"表达微弱希望，体现轻微惊讶（对可能性的意外），故调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感转折（从绝望到微弱希望）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"行动设想结束，中等停顿连接实际行为\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 630, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，630 tokens匹配稍快语速表现期待\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 22, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (25, 4, '{\"text\": \"最后她抽出一根来了。哧！它燃起来了，冒出火光来了！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"拟声词\'哧\'与火光出现体现惊讶，故调整维度6为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感转折（惊讶），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感转折处（从寒冷到温暖幻觉），延长停顿突出变化\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配稍快语速表现惊喜\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 23, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (26, 4, '{\"text\": \"当她把手覆在上面的时候，小姑娘觉得真像坐在一个铁火炉旁边一样：它有光亮的黄铜圆捏手和黄铜炉身。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述温暖幻觉体现高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"冒号后为完整描述，情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"幻觉描述结束，中等停顿连接后续细节\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"46字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 24, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (27, 4, '{\"text\": \"火烧得那么欢，那么暖，那么美！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"重复强调\'欢、暖、美\'体现强烈高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感强烈（高兴），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮处，延长停顿强调温暖感受\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，500 tokens匹配轻快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 25, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (28, 4, '{\"text\": \"唉，这是怎么一回事？当小姑娘刚刚伸出一双脚、打算暖一暖脚的时候，火焰就忽然熄灭了！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"混合惊讶(0.2)与悲伤(0.3)，总和0.5达上限，因火焰突然熄灭\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感转折（惊讶混合悲伤），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感转折处（从高兴到悲伤），延长停顿突出失落感\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 26, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (29, 4, '{\"text\": \"火炉也不见了。她坐在那儿，手中只有烧过了的火柴。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述幻觉消失后的现实，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"现实描述结束，稍长停顿连接下一次尝试\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 27, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (30, 4, '{\"text\": \"她又擦了一根。它燃起来了，发出光来了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"重复点火动作体现微弱希望，故调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（微弱惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"动作结束，中等停顿连接幻觉内容\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"22字短文本，550 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 28, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (31, 4, '{\"text\": \"墙上有亮光照着的那块地方，现在变得透明，像一片薄纱；她可以看到房间里的东西：桌上铺着雪白的台布，上面有精致的碗盘，填满了梅子和苹果的、冒着香气的烤鹅。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述丰盛食物体现微弱高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"冒号后为完整描述，情感一致（微弱高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"幻觉描述结束，中等停顿连接动态场景\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 850, \"duration_reason\": \"62字较长文本，850 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 29, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (32, 4, '{\"text\": \"更美妙的事情是：这只鹅从盘子里跳出来了，背上插着刀叉，蹒跚地在地上走着，一直向这个穷苦的小姑娘面前走来。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.1, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"动态食物幻觉体现强烈高兴(0.3)混合轻微惊讶(0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴混合惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"幻觉高潮结束，延长停顿突出戏剧性\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"54字较长文本，800 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 30, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (33, 4, '{\"text\": \"这时火柴就熄灭了；她面前只有一堵又厚又冷的墙。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"幻觉消失回到现实，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.2)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"分号连接的完整句，情感转折符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感转折处（从幻觉到冰冷现实），延长停顿强调绝望\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 31, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (34, 4, '{\"text\": \"她点了另一根火柴。现在她是坐在美丽的圣诞树下面。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述圣诞树幻觉体现微弱高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（微弱高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"新幻觉开始，中等停顿建立场景\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 32, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (35, 4, '{\"text\": \"上次圣诞节时，她透过玻璃门，看到一个富有商人家里的一株圣诞树；可是现在这一株比那株还要大，还要美。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"比较强调\'更大更美\'体现高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"分号连接的完整句，情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"描述结束，中等停顿连接细节\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"46字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 33, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (36, 4, '{\"text\": \"它的绿枝上燃着几千支蜡烛；彩色的图画，跟橱窗里挂着的那些一样美丽，在向她眨眼。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.1, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"动态描述\'眨眼\'体现高兴(0.3)混合轻微惊讶(0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"分号连接的完整句，情感一致（高兴混合惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"幻觉高潮结束，延长停顿突出美好\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 34, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (37, 4, '{\"text\": \"这个小姑娘把两只手伸过去。于是火柴就灭了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"幻觉再次消失，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.2)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折（悲伤混合忧郁），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感转折处（从美好到失落），延长停顿强调循环绝望\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，550 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 35, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (38, 4, '{\"text\": \"圣诞节的烛光越升越高。她看到它们现在变成了明亮的星星。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述烛光变星星体现轻微惊讶，故调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（微弱惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"幻觉转换结束，中等停顿连接天文现象\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 36, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (39, 4, '{\"text\": \"这些星星有一颗落下来了，在天上划出一条长长的光线。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述流星划过体现惊讶情绪，故调整维度6为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"天文现象描述结束，稍长停顿连接文化解释\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 630, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，630 tokens匹配稍快语速表现动态\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 37, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (40, 4, '{\"text\": \"“现在又有一个什么人死去了，”小姑娘说，因为她的老祖母曾经说过：天上落下一颗星，地上就有一个灵魂升到上帝那儿去。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及死亡与祖母回忆，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"重要回忆结束，延长停顿强调情感连接\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"56字较长文本，800 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 38, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (41, 4, '{\"text\": \"老祖母是唯一对她好的人，但是现在已经死了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"直接陈述祖母去世，混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.2)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键情感信息结束，延长停顿强化失落感\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 39, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (42, 4, '{\"text\": \"她在墙上又擦了一根火柴。它把四周都照亮了；在这亮光中老祖母出现了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.1, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"祖母出现带来温暖希望，混合高兴(0.2)与轻微惊讶(0.1)，总和0.3符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"分号连接的完整句，情感转折（从悲伤到希望），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键人物出现，延长停顿突出情感转折\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 40, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (43, 4, '{\"text\": \"她显得那么光明，那么温柔，那么和蔼。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"重复强调祖母美好特质，体现强烈高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮描述结束，稍长停顿连接呼唤\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，500 tokens匹配轻快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 41, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (44, 4, '{\"text\": \"“祖母！”小姑娘叫起来，“啊！请把我带走吧！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.8, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0.1, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"急切呼唤混合高兴(0.2)、悲伤(0.1)、害怕(0.1)、惊讶(0.1)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感复杂交织，符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮对话，延长停顿增强紧迫感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"22字短对话文本，550 tokens匹配急切语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 42, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (45, 4, '{\"text\": \"我知道，这火柴一灭掉，你就会不见了，你就会像那个温暖的火炉，那只美丽的烤鹅，那棵幸福的圣诞树一样地不见了！”\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.8, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0.1, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"表达恐惧失去祖母，混合悲伤(0.3)、害怕(0.1)、忧郁(0.1)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感强烈（混合负面情绪），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮对话结束，延长停顿连接行动\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"52字较长对话文本，800 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 43, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (46, 4, '{\"text\": \"于是她急忙把整束火柴中剩下的火柴都擦亮了，因为她非常想把祖母留住。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0.1, 0.1, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"急切行动混合希望(0.2)与恐惧(0.1+0.1)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（混合情绪），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键行动结束，延长停顿连接结果\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"40字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配稍快语速表现急切\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 44, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (47, 4, '{\"text\": \"这些火柴发出强烈的光芒，照得比大白天还要明朗。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述强烈光芒体现高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"光明描述结束，稍长停顿连接祖母形象\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 630, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，630 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 45, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (48, 4, '{\"text\": \"祖母从来没有像现在这样显得美丽和高大。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"强调祖母美好形象体现高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"形象描述结束，稍长停顿连接拥抱动作\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"22字短文本，550 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 46, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (49, 4, '{\"text\": \"她把小姑娘抱起来，搂到怀里。她们两人在光明和快乐中飞走了，越飞越高，飞到既没有寒冷，也没有饥饿，也没有忧愁的那块地方——她们是跟上帝在一起。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述解脱与幸福体现高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"破折号后为完整结局，情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"故事高潮结束，延长停顿营造神圣感\", \"interval_silence\": 600}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 850, \"duration_reason\": \"62字较长文本，850 tokens匹配舒缓语速营造升华感\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 47, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (50, 4, '{\"text\": \"不过在一个寒冷的清晨，这个小姑娘却坐在一个墙角里；她的双颊通红，嘴唇发出微笑，她已经死了——在旧年的除夕冻死了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述死亡现实混合悲伤(0.3)与忧郁(0.2)，总和0.5达上限\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"破折号后为完整结局，情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"悲剧结局揭示，延长停顿增强冲击力\", \"interval_silence\": 600}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 850, \"duration_reason\": \"58字较长文本，850 tokens匹配缓慢语速表现沉重\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 48, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (51, 4, '{\"text\": \"新年的太阳升起来了，照着她小小的尸体！\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对比新年阳光与死亡，体现悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"感叹号结尾且情感强烈（悲伤），符合最高优先级规则\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"强烈对比结束，延长停顿强调悲剧性\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"22字短文本，550 tokens匹配缓慢语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 49, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (52, 4, '{\"text\": \"她坐在那儿，手中还捏着火柴——其中有一扎差不多都烧光了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述遗物体现悲伤(0.2)与忧郁(0.1)，总和0.3符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（悲伤混合忧郁），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"细节描述结束，稍长停顿连接他人反应\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 50, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (53, 4, '{\"text\": \"“她想把自己暖和一下。”人们说。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"他人简单解释体现对悲剧的无知，隐含悲伤情绪，故调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（隐含悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"他人话语结束，稍长停顿连接真相揭示\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短对话文本，500 tokens匹配平稳语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 51, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (54, 4, '{\"text\": \"谁也不知道：她曾经看到过多么美丽的东西，她曾经是多么光荣地跟祖母一起，走到新年的幸福中去。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"结尾强调美好幻觉，体现微弱高兴情绪，故调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且为故事结尾，情感升华（微弱高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"故事最终结尾，大幅延长停顿增强收尾感\", \"interval_silence\": 700}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"52字较长结尾文本，800 tokens匹配舒缓语速营造余韵\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 52, '2025-10-27 16:43:22', '2025-10-27 16:43:22', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (55, 5, '{\"text\": \"从前有个可爱的小姑娘，谁见了都喜欢，但最喜欢她的是她的奶奶，简直是她要什么就给她什么。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无明显情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 740, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，740 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 1, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (56, 5, '{\"text\": \"一次，奶奶送给小姑娘一顶用丝绒做的小红帽，戴在她的头上正好合适。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"奶奶送礼物体现轻微高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"31字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配轻快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 2, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (57, 5, '{\"text\": \"从此，姑娘再也不愿意戴任何别的帽子，于是大家便叫她\\\"小红帽\\\"。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 670, \"duration_reason\": \"29字中等长度文本，670 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 3, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (58, 5, '{\"text\": \"一天，妈妈对小红帽说：\\\"来，小红帽，这里有一块蛋糕和一瓶葡萄酒，快给奶奶送去，奶奶生病了，身子很虚弱，吃了这些就会好一些的。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及奶奶生病体现轻微悲伤情绪，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容过长（58字），按逗号拆分保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话未结束（逗号连接），短暂停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 820, \"duration_reason\": \"58字较长对话文本，820 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 4, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (59, 5, '{\"text\": \"趁着现在天还没有热，赶紧动身吧。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话中间逗号拆分，短暂停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，580 tokens匹配对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 5, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (60, 5, '{\"text\": \"在路上要好好走，不要跑，也不要离开大路，否则你会摔跤的，那样奶奶就什么也吃不上了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及奶奶吃不上体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.1\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话中间逗号拆分，短暂停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 760, \"duration_reason\": \"41字中等长度对话文本，760 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 6, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (61, 5, '{\"text\": \"到奶奶家的时候，别忘了说\'早上好\'，也不要一进屋就东瞧西瞅。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到回应\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 690, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度对话文本，690 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 7, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (62, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"我会小心的。\\\"小红帽对妈妈说，并且还和妈妈拉手作保证。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无明显情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 660, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，660 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 8, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (63, 5, '{\"text\": \"奶奶住在村子外面的森林里，离小红帽家有很长一段路。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"27字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 9, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (64, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽刚走进森林就碰到了一条狼。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"遇到狼可能引发轻微害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折（平静到轻微害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节转折点（进入森林遇狼），中等停顿强调变化\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 590, \"duration_reason\": \"19字短文本，590 tokens匹配稍快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 10, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (65, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽不知道狼是坏家伙，所以一点也不怕它。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"文本明确说明\'一点也不怕\'，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 640, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，640 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 11, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (66, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"你好，小红帽，\\\"狼说。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 520, \"duration_reason\": \"10字短对话文本，520 tokens匹配轻快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 12, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (67, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"谢谢你，狼先生。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 480, \"duration_reason\": \"7字极短对话文本，480 tokens避免拖沓\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 13, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (68, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"小红帽，这么早要到哪里去呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 530, \"duration_reason\": \"12字短对话文本，530 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 14, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (69, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"我要到奶奶家去。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 470, \"duration_reason\": \"8字极短对话文本，470 tokens避免拖沓\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 15, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (70, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"你那围裙下面有什么呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 510, \"duration_reason\": \"11字短对话文本，510 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 16, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (71, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"蛋糕和葡萄酒。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话未结束（逗号连接），极短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 490, \"duration_reason\": \"6字极短对话文本，490 tokens避免拖沓\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 17, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (72, 5, '{\"text\": \"昨天我们家烤了一些蛋糕，可怜的奶奶生了病，要吃一些好东西才能恢复过来。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及奶奶生病体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到新对话轮次\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度对话文本，720 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 18, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (73, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"你奶奶住在哪里呀，小红帽？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 540, \"duration_reason\": \"13字短对话文本，540 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 19, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (74, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"进了林子还有一段路呢。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话未结束（逗号连接），极短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 560, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短对话文本，560 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 20, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (75, 5, '{\"text\": \"她的房子就在三棵大橡树下，低处围着核桃树篱笆。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话未结束（逗号连接），极短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，680 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 21, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (76, 5, '{\"text\": \"你一定知道的。\\\"小红帽说。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到叙述部分\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 570, \"duration_reason\": \"15字短文本，570 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 22, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (77, 5, '{\"text\": \"狼在心中盘算着：\\\"这小东西细皮嫩肉的，味道肯定比那老太婆要好。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼的内心独白体现愤怒/恶意，调整维度1为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话内容按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话未结束（逗号连接），极短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"35字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配稍慢语速强调恶意\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 23, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (78, 5, '{\"text\": \"我要讲究一下策略，让她俩都逃不出我的手心。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼的内心独白体现愤怒/恶意，调整维度1为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"恶意独白结束，延长停顿强调危险性\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配稍慢语速强调恶意\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 24, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (79, 5, '{\"text\": \"于是它陪着小红帽走了一会儿，然后说：\\\"小红帽，你看周围这些花多么美丽啊！干吗不回头看一看呢？还有这些小鸟，它们唱得多么动听啊！你大概根本没有听到吧？林子里的一切多么美好啊，而你却只管往前走，就像是去上学一样。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼假装赞美体现虚假高兴，调整维度0为0.2（实际为欺骗）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整（85字未超限）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到小红帽反应\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 920, \"duration_reason\": \"85字长对话文本，920 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 25, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (80, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽抬起头来，看到阳光在树木间来回跳荡，美丽的鲜花在四周开放，便想：\\\"也许我该摘一把鲜花给奶奶，让她高兴高兴。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"想让奶奶高兴体现轻微高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白按逗号拆分，保持语义连贯\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白未结束（逗号连接），极短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 840, \"duration_reason\": \"53字较长文本，840 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 26, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (81, 5, '{\"text\": \"现在天色还早，我不会去迟的。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"内心独白无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 27, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (82, 5, '{\"text\": \"她于是离开大路，走进林子去采花。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 610, \"duration_reason\": \"21字中等长度文本，610 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 28, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (83, 5, '{\"text\": \"她每采下一朵花，总觉得前面还有更美丽的花朵，便又向前走去，结果一直走到了林子深处。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景转换（从采花到深入森林），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节转折点（进入林子深处），延长停顿强调危险临近\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 740, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，740 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 29, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (84, 5, '{\"text\": \"就在此时，狼却直接跑到奶奶家，敲了敲门。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 660, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，660 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 30, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (85, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"是谁呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短暂停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 450, \"duration_reason\": \"5字极短对话文本，450 tokens避免拖沓\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 31, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (86, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"是小红帽。\\\"狼回答，\\\"我给你送蛋糕和葡萄酒来了。快开门哪。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到奶奶回应\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 710, \"duration_reason\": \"33字中等长度对话文本，710 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 32, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (87, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"你拉一下门栓就行了，\\\"奶奶大声说，\\\"我身上没有力气，起不来。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"奶奶生病无力体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"危险临近（奶奶虚弱），延长停顿增强紧张感\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度对话文本，700 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 33, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (88, 5, '{\"text\": \"狼刚拉起门栓，那门就开了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，580 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 34, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (89, 5, '{\"text\": \"狼二话没说就冲到奶奶的床前，把奶奶吞进了肚子。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"奶奶被吞体现悲伤情绪，调整维度2为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感高潮（悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节高潮（奶奶被吞），延长停顿增强冲击力\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配稍慢语速强调严重性\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 35, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (90, 5, '{\"text\": \"然后她穿上奶奶的衣服，戴上她的帽子，躺在床上，还拉上了帘子。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景转换（狼伪装完成），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"伪装完成，中等停顿过渡到小红帽行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 730, \"duration_reason\": \"33字中等长度文本，730 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 36, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (91, 5, '{\"text\": \"可这时小红帽还在跑来跑去地采花。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 37, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (92, 5, '{\"text\": \"直到采了许多许多，她都拿不了啦，她才想起奶奶，重新上路去奶奶家。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 740, \"duration_reason\": \"36字中等长度文本，740 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 38, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (93, 5, '{\"text\": \"看到奶奶家的屋门敞开着，她感到很奇怪。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"感到奇怪体现轻微害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感转折（平静到轻微害怕），中等停顿强调变化\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 640, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，640 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 39, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (94, 5, '{\"text\": \"她一走进屋子就有一种异样的感觉，心中便想：\\\"天哪！平常我那么喜欢来奶奶家，今天怎么这样害怕？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"内心独白明确表达害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"害怕情绪高潮，延长停顿增强紧张感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"48字较长文本，800 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 40, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (95, 5, '{\"text\": \"她大声叫道：\\\"早上好！\\\"，可是没有听到回答。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"没有回应加剧害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"紧张情节（无回应），延长停顿增强悬念\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"29字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 41, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (96, 5, '{\"text\": \"她走到床前拉开帘子，只见奶奶躺在床上，帽子拉得低低的，把脸都遮住了，样子非常奇怪。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"样子奇怪加剧害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感高潮（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"紧张情节高潮（发现异常），延长停顿增强悬念\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 820, \"duration_reason\": \"49字较长文本，820 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 42, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (97, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"哎，奶奶，\\\"她说，\\\"你的耳朵怎么这样大呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现异常体现害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 670, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，670 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 43, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (98, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"为了更好地听你说话呀，乖乖。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装对话无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"20字短对话文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 44, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (99, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"可是奶奶，你的眼睛怎么这样大呀？\\\"小红帽又问。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现异常体现害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"29字中等长度对话文本，680 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 45, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (100, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"为了更清楚地看你呀，乖乖。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装对话无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"20字短对话文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 46, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (101, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"奶奶，你的手怎么这样大呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现异常体现害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 590, \"duration_reason\": \"19字短对话文本，590 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 47, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (102, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"可以更好地抱着你呀。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装对话无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿保持节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 560, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短对话文本，560 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 48, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (103, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"奶奶，你的嘴巴怎么大得很吓人呀？\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"明确表达害怕（\'吓人\'），调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且情感高潮（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"害怕情绪高潮，延长停顿强调危险\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度对话文本，620 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 49, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (104, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"可以一口把你吃掉呀！\\\"狼刚把话说完，就从床上跳起来，把小红帽吞进了肚子，狼满足了食欲之后便重新躺到床上睡觉，而且鼾声震天。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼暴露恶意体现愤怒，调整维度1为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感高潮（愤怒），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节高潮（小红帽被吞），延长停顿增强冲击力\", \"interval_silence\": 550}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 880, \"duration_reason\": \"62字长文本，880 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 50, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (105, 5, '{\"text\": \"一位猎人碰巧从屋前走过，心想：\\\"这老太太鼾打得好响啊！我要进去看看她是不是出什么事了。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"猎人发现异常体现惊讶，调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节转折（猎人出现），中等停顿强调变化\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 820, \"duration_reason\": \"52字较长文本，820 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 51, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (106, 5, '{\"text\": \"猎人进了屋，来到床前时却发现躺在那里的竟是狼。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现真相体现惊讶，调整维度6为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感高潮（惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"惊讶情绪高潮，延长停顿增强冲击力\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配稍快语速强调惊讶\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 52, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (107, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"你这老坏蛋，我找了你这么久，真没想到在这里找到你！\\\"他说。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"猎人愤怒体现，调整维度1为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 760, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度对话文本，760 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 53, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (108, 5, '{\"text\": \"他正准备向狼开枪，突然又想到，这狼很可能把奶奶吞进了肚子，奶奶也许还活着。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"担心奶奶体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（担忧），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节转折（改变计划），中等停顿强调变化\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 800, \"duration_reason\": \"47字较长文本，800 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 54, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (109, 5, '{\"text\": \"猎人就没有开枪，而是操起一把剪刀，动手把呼呼大睡的狼的肚子剪了开来。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景转换（救援开始），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"救援行动开始，中等停顿强调转折\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 780, \"duration_reason\": \"43字中等长度文本，780 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 55, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (110, 5, '{\"text\": \"他刚剪了两下，就看到了红色的小帽子。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现小红帽体现惊讶，调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折（平静到惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"发现关键物品，中等停顿强调希望\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 660, \"duration_reason\": \"27字中等长度文本，660 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 56, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (111, 5, '{\"text\": \"他又剪了两下，小姑娘便跳了出来，叫道：\\\"真把我吓坏了！狼肚子里黑漆漆的。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"小红帽明确表达害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"害怕情绪表达，延长停顿增强代入感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 780, \"duration_reason\": \"43字中等长度文本，780 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 57, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (112, 5, '{\"text\": \"接着，奶奶也活着出来了，只是有点喘不过气来。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"奶奶获救体现轻微高兴，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折（悲伤到高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"救援成功，中等停顿过渡到后续行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 58, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (113, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽赶紧跑去搬来几块大石头，塞进狼的肚子。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 59, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (114, 5, '{\"text\": \"狼醒来之后想逃走，可是那些石头太重了，它刚站起来就跌到在地，摔死了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景结束（狼死亡），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"反派结局，中等停顿强调正义\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 760, \"duration_reason\": \"41字中等长度文本，760 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 60, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (115, 5, '{\"text\": \"三个人高兴极了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"明确表达高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感高潮（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情感高潮（高兴），中等停顿强调喜悦\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 520, \"duration_reason\": \"8字极短文本，520 tokens避免拖沓\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 61, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (116, 5, '{\"text\": \"猎人剥下狼皮，回家去了；奶奶吃了小红帽带来的蛋糕和葡萄酒，精神好多了；而小红帽却在想：\\\"要是妈妈不允许，我一辈子也不独自离开大路，跑进森林了。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"结尾总结无强烈情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且为故事主要结局，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"故事主要结局，延长停顿增强收尾感\", \"interval_silence\": 600}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 900, \"duration_reason\": \"78字长文本，900 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 62, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (117, 5, '{\"text\": \"人们还说，小红帽后来又有一次把蛋糕送给奶奶，而且在路上又有一只狼跟她搭话，想骗她离开大路。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 840, \"duration_reason\": \"54字较长文本，840 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 63, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (118, 5, '{\"text\": \"可小红帽这次提高了警惕，头也不回地向前走。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 64, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (119, 5, '{\"text\": \"她告诉奶奶她碰到了狼，那家伙嘴上虽然对她说\\\"你好\\\"，眼睛里却露着凶光，要不是在大路上，它准把她给吃了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及狼的凶光体现轻微害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（轻微害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"危险回忆，中等停顿强调警惕性\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 860, \"duration_reason\": \"58字较长文本，860 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 65, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (120, 5, '{\"text\": \"\\\"那么，\\\"奶奶说，\\\"我们把门关紧，不让它进来。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，680 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 66, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (121, 5, '{\"text\": \"不一会儿，狼真的一面敲着门一面叫道：\\\"奶奶，快开门呀。我是小红帽，给你送蛋糕来了。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装对话无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到拒绝回应\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 820, \"duration_reason\": \"50字较长对话文本，820 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 67, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (122, 5, '{\"text\": \"但是她们既不说话，也不开门。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，580 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 68, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (123, 5, '{\"text\": \"这长着灰毛的家伙围着房子转了两三圈，最后跳上屋顶，打算等小红帽在傍晚回家时偷偷跟在她的后面，趁天黑把她吃掉。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼的恶意计划体现愤怒，调整维度1为0.3（儿童故事中适度表达）\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（愤怒），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"危险计划，延长停顿强调威胁\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 920, \"duration_reason\": \"72字长文本，920 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 69, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (124, 5, '{\"text\": \"可奶奶看穿了这家伙的坏心思。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"20字短文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 70, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (125, 5, '{\"text\": \"她想起屋子前有一个大石头槽子，便对小姑娘说：\\\"小红帽，把桶拿来。我昨天做了一些香肠，提些煮香肠的水去倒进石头槽里。\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且引号闭合，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 900, \"duration_reason\": \"68字长对话文本，900 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 71, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (126, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽提了很多很多水，把那个大石头槽子装得满满的。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 72, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (127, 5, '{\"text\": \"香肠的气味飘进了狼的鼻孔，它使劲地用鼻子闻呀闻，并且朝下张望着，到最后把脖子伸得太长了，身子开始往下滑。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景转换（狼上当），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"情节转折（狼上当），中等停顿强调变化\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 880, \"duration_reason\": \"60字较长文本，880 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 73, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (128, 5, '{\"text\": \"它从屋顶上滑了下来，正好落在大石槽中，淹死了。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性文本无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且场景结束（狼死亡），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"反派结局，中等停顿强调正义\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 74, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (129, 5, '{\"text\": \"小红帽高高兴兴地回了家，从此再也没有谁伤害过她。\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"结尾明确表达高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且为故事最终结局，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"故事最终结尾，延长停顿增强收尾感\", \"interval_silence\": 800}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度结尾文本，720 tokens匹配舒缓语速营造温馨感\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 75, '2025-10-28 11:31:41', '2025-10-28 11:31:41', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (130, 6, '{\"text\": \"Once upon a time there was a sweet little girl.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述性开头，无明确情感词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事流畅性\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"12字短文本，580 tokens匹配轻快自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 1, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (131, 6, '{\"text\": \"Everyone who saw her liked her, but most of all her grandmother, who did not know what to give the child next.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述祖母疼爱，但无强烈情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿，保持叙事节奏\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 740, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度文本，740 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 2, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (132, 6, '{\"text\": \"Once she gave her a little cap made of red velvet.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"中性叙述，无情感倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，620 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 3, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (133, 6, '{\"text\": \"Because it suited her so well, and she wanted to wear it all the time, she came to be known as Little Red Riding Hood.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"解释名字由来，无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且语义完整（名字确立），情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾且为角色命名完成，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"36字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 4, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (134, 6, '{\"text\": \"One day her mother said to her: \\\"Come Little Red Riding Hood.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话开始，语气温和但无强烈情绪，使用零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点（逗号后引号内），语义未完但长度适中\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部逗号拆分，短停顿保持连贯性\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短对话文本，550 tokens匹配自然说话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 5, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (135, 6, '{\"text\": \"Here is a piece of cake and a bottle of wine.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"母亲给予物品，语气平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整短句，情感一致（平静）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部句号，短停顿保持连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"15字短文本，580 tokens匹配对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 6, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (136, 6, '{\"text\": \"Take them to your grandmother.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"指令性对话，无情绪词，使用零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整指令句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话指令短句，短停顿衔接下文\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"8字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 7, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (137, 6, '{\"text\": \"She is sick and weak, and they will do her well.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及\'生病虚弱\'体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"情感一致（轻微悲伤），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"涉及祖母病情，稍长停顿表达关切\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 8, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (138, 6, '{\"text\": \"Mind your manners and give her my greetings.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"母亲叮嘱，语气平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整叮嘱句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部句号，短停顿保持连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"13字短文本，580 tokens匹配对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 9, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (139, 6, '{\"text\": \"Behave yourself on the way, and do not leave the path, or you might fall down and break the glass, and then there will be nothing for your sick grandmother.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"再次提及\'生病祖母\'及后果，维持轻微悲伤情绪\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且情感一致（轻微悲伤）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"母亲叮嘱结束，中等停顿强调重要性\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度对话文本，750 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 10, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (140, 6, '{\"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood promised to obey her mother.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述承诺，无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 11, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (141, 6, '{\"text\": \"The grandmother lived out in the woods, a half hour from the village.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"场景描述，无情绪倾向，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且语义完整（地点说明）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"20字短文本上限，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 12, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (142, 6, '{\"text\": \"When Little Red Riding Hood entered the woods a wolf came up to her.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"出现狼但女孩不害怕，隐含轻微紧张，调整维度3为0.1\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（轻微紧张）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"引入潜在危险角色，稍长停顿营造氛围\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 13, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (143, 6, '{\"text\": \"She did not know what a wicked animal he was, and was not afraid of him.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"强调女孩无惧，整体平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 14, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (144, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Good day to you, Little Red Riding Hood.\\\" - \\\"Thank you, wolf.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"礼貌对话，无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次，情感一致（平静）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短停顿衔接下一轮\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短对话文本，650 tokens匹配自然对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 15, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (145, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Where are you going so early, Little Red Riding Hood?\\\" - \\\"To grandmother\'s.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"问答对话，语气中性，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整问答轮次，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短停顿衔接下一轮\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 630, \"duration_reason\": \"17字短对话文本，630 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 16, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (146, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"And what are you carrying under your apron?\\\" - \\\"Grandmother is sick and weak, and I am taking her some cake and wine.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"提及祖母生病，体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点（逗号后引号内），情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部逗号拆分，短停顿保持连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度对话文本，750 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 17, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (147, 6, '{\"text\": \"We baked yesterday, and they should give her strength.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续祖母生病话题，维持轻微悲伤情绪\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且情感一致（轻微悲伤）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，600 tokens匹配对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 18, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (148, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Little Red Riding Hood, just where does your grandmother live?\\\" - \\\"Her house is a good quarter hour from here in the woods, under the three large oak trees.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"询问地址的中性对话，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点（逗号后引号内），情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部逗号拆分，短停顿保持连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"40字中等长度对话文本，750 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 19, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (149, 6, '{\"text\": \"There\'s a hedge of hazel bushes there. You must know the place,\\\" said Little Red Riding Hood.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述地址，语气平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束且为重要信息，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 20, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (150, 6, '{\"text\": \"The wolf thought to himself: \\\"Now there is a tasty bite for me.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼内心独白含\'美味\'和恶意，轻微愤怒(0.1)与厌恶(0.1)，总和0.2符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白自然停顿点，情感一致（负面）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白内部逗号拆分，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配稍快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 21, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (151, 6, '{\"text\": \"Just how are you going to catch her?\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续狼的恶意计划，维持轻微愤怒与厌恶\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"10字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 22, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (152, 6, '{\"text\": \"Then he said: \\\"Listen, Little Red Riding Hood, haven\'t you seen the beautiful flowers that are blossoming in the woods?\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装友好，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点（问号后引号内），情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部问号，短停顿保持连贯\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"36字中等长度对话文本，750 tokens保证清晰表达\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 23, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (153, 6, '{\"text\": \"Why don\'t you go and take a look?\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"诱导性提问，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整问句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部问号，短停顿衔接下句\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"9字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 24, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (154, 6, '{\"text\": \"And I don\'t believe you can hear how beautifully the birds are singing.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼继续伪装赞美，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部句号，短停顿衔接下句\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 25, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (155, 6, '{\"text\": \"You are walking along as though you were on your way to school in the village.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼的伪装评价，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部句号，短停顿衔接下句\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 26, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (156, 6, '{\"text\": \"It is very beautiful in the woods.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼结束诱导，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到女孩反应\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"10字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 27, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (157, 6, '{\"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood opened her eyes and saw the sunlight breaking through the trees and how the ground was covered with beautiful flowers.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述美丽景色引发高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 28, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (158, 6, '{\"text\": \"She thought: \\\"If a take a bouquet to grandmother, she will be very pleased.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"女孩想让祖母高兴，延续轻微高兴情绪\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白自然停顿点，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白内部逗号拆分，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 29, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (159, 6, '{\"text\": \"Anyway, it is still early, and I\'ll be home on time.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"女孩自我安慰，维持轻微高兴情绪\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，600 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 30, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (160, 6, '{\"text\": \"And she ran off into the woods looking for flowers.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"行动体现高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，620 tokens匹配轻快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 31, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (161, 6, '{\"text\": \"Each time she picked one she thought that she could see an even more beautiful one a little way off, and she ran after it, going further and further into the woods.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"持续寻找花朵体现高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"段落结束且暗示危险临近，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"46字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 32, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (162, 6, '{\"text\": \"But the wolf ran straight to the grandmother\'s house and knocked on the door.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼行动体现恶意，轻微愤怒(0.1)与厌恶(0.1)，总和0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"行动描述结束，中等停顿过渡到对话\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配稍快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 33, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (163, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Who\'s there?\\\" - \\\"Little Red Riding Hood.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"伪装对话，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部逗号拆分，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"12字短对话文本，500 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 34, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (164, 6, '{\"text\": \"I\'m bringing you some cake and wine.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装送礼，表面平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中完整句，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部句号，短停顿衔接下句\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"12字短文本，550 tokens匹配对话节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 35, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (165, 6, '{\"text\": \"Open the door for me.\\\" - \\\"Just press the latch,\\\" called out the grandmother.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"祖母虚弱回应，体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次，情感一致（轻微悲伤）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，短停顿衔接下句\", \"interval_silence\": 250}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，680 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 36, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (166, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"I\'m too weak to get up.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"祖母明确表达虚弱，悲伤情绪加强，调整维度2为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且情感一致（悲伤）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"祖母虚弱陈述结束，中等停顿强调危险\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"9字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 37, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (167, 6, '{\"text\": \"The wolf pressed the latch, and the door opened.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼得逞行动，维持轻微愤怒与厌恶\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键行动完成，稍长停顿营造紧张感\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 600, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，600 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 38, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (168, 6, '{\"text\": \"He stepped inside, went straight to the grandmother\'s bed, and ate her up.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.8, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"暴力行为体现较强愤怒(0.2)与厌恶(0.2)，总和0.4符合限制\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（强烈负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"暴力行为结束，延长停顿强调严重性\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 680, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，680 tokens匹配稍快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 39, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (169, 6, '{\"text\": \"Then he took her clothes, put them on, and put her cap on his head.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼伪装行为，维持轻微愤怒与厌恶\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"伪装完成，中等停顿过渡到等待\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 40, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (170, 6, '{\"text\": \"He got into her bed and pulled the curtains shut.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼完成伪装，维持轻微愤怒与厌恶\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"场景设置完成，稍长停顿营造悬念\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 41, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (171, 6, '{\"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood had run after flowers, and did not continue on her way to grandmother\'s until she had gathered all that she could carry.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述女孩行动，无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"段落结束，常规停顿过渡到新场景\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 42, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (172, 6, '{\"text\": \"When she arrived, she found, to her surprise, that the door was open.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"文本含\'惊讶\'，体现惊讶情绪，调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"情感转折（平静到惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"发现异常，中等停顿强调惊讶\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"24字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 43, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (173, 6, '{\"text\": \"She walked into the parlor, and everything looked so strange that she thought: \\\"Oh, my God, why am I so afraid?\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"文本含\'害怕\'，体现害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白自然停顿点，情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白内部问号，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 44, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (174, 6, '{\"text\": \"I usually like it at grandmother\'s.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短文本，550 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 45, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (175, 6, '{\"text\": \"Then she went to the bed and pulled back the curtains.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"行动体现紧张害怕，调整维度3为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键行动前，稍长停顿营造悬念\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，650 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 46, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (176, 6, '{\"text\": \"Grandmother was lying there with her cap pulled down over her face and looking very strange.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"描述异常外观引发害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（害怕），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"异常发现，延长停顿强调紧张感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 47, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (177, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Oh, grandmother, what big ears you have!\\\" - \\\"All the better to hear you with.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话体现女孩害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次，情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，700 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 48, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (178, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Oh, grandmother, what big eyes you have!\\\" - \\\"All the better to see you with.\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次，情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话轮次结束，常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，700 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 49, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (179, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Oh, grandmother, what big hands you have!\\\" - \\\"All the better to grab you with!\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话紧张升级，维持害怕情绪\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次，情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话威胁性增强，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度对话文本，700 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 50, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (180, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"Oh, grandmother, what a horribly big mouth you have!\\\" - \\\"All the better to eat you with!\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.8, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"对话高潮体现强烈害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"完整对话轮次且情感高潮，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话高潮结束，延长停顿强调危险\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度对话文本，720 tokens匹配紧张节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 51, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (181, 6, '{\"text\": \"And with that he jumped out of bed, jumped on top of poor Little Red Riding Hood, and ate her up.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.8, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"暴力行为体现较强愤怒(0.2)与厌恶(0.2)，总和0.4\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（强烈负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"悲剧高潮结束，延长停顿营造沉重感\", \"interval_silence\": 600}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"32字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配稍快语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 52, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (182, 6, '{\"text\": \"As soon as the wolf had finished this tasty bite, he climbed back into bed, fell asleep, and began to snore very loudly.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"狼满足后休息，维持轻微愤怒与厌恶\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（负面），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"场景转换，中等停顿引入新角色\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"38字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 53, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (183, 6, '{\"text\": \"A huntsman was just passing by.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.65, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"引入新角色，叙述平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"9字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 54, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (184, 6, '{\"text\": \"He thought it strange that the old woman was snoring so loudly, so he decided to take a look.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"猎人发现异常，体现轻微惊讶，调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（轻微惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"决定行动前，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"28字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 55, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (185, 6, '{\"text\": \"He stepped inside, and in the bed there lay the wolf that he had been hunting for such a long time.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现目标狼，体现惊讶情绪，调整维度6为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键发现，中等停顿强调重要性\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"34字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 56, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (186, 6, '{\"text\": \"\\\"He has eaten the grandmother, but perhaps she still can be saved.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"猎人内心担忧祖母，体现轻微悲伤，调整维度2为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白自然停顿点，情感一致\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白内部逗号拆分，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 650, \"duration_reason\": \"22字中等长度文本，650 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 57, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (187, 6, '{\"text\": \"I won\'t shoot him,\\\" thought the huntsman.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续担忧情绪，维持轻微悲伤\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"内心独白结束且情感一致（轻微悲伤）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"内心独白结束，中等停顿过渡到行动\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 550, \"duration_reason\": \"14字短文本，550 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 58, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (188, 6, '{\"text\": \"So he took a pair of scissors and cut open his belly.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"救援行动，语气专注但无强烈情绪，使用零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静专注），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键行动，稍长停顿营造紧张感\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 59, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (189, 6, '{\"text\": \"He had cut only a few strokes when he saw the red cap shining through.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.2, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"发现红帽体现惊讶，调整维度6为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（惊讶），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"关键发现，稍长停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 350}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 700, \"duration_reason\": \"26字中等长度文本，700 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 60, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (190, 6, '{\"text\": \"He cut a little more, and the girl jumped out and cried: \\\"Oh, I was so frightened!\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"女孩表达害怕，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话中自然停顿点，情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话内部感叹号，短停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 200}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 720, \"duration_reason\": \"30字中等长度文本，720 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 61, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (191, 6, '{\"text\": \"It was so dark inside the wolf\'s body!\\\"\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"延续害怕情绪，调整维度3为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"对话轮次结束且情感一致（害怕）\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"对话结束，中等停顿过渡到祖母\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 580, \"duration_reason\": \"16字短文本，580 tokens匹配自然节奏\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 62, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (192, 6, '{\"text\": \"And then the grandmother came out alive as well.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"祖母获救体现高兴情绪，调整维度0为0.2\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感转折（悲伤到高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"积极转折，稍长停顿强调喜悦\", \"interval_silence\": 450}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 63, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (193, 6, '{\"text\": \"Then Little Red Riding Hood fetched some large heavy stones.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"行动描述，无情绪词，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（平静），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"句号结尾常规停顿\", \"interval_silence\": 300}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 620, \"duration_reason\": \"18字短文本，620 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 64, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (194, 6, '{\"text\": \"They filled the wolf\'s body with them, and when he woke up and tried to run away, the stones were so heavy that he fell down dead.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.7, \"emo_vector\": [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"叙述结局，语气平静，使用默认零向量\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且为故事高潮结束，语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"故事高潮结束，延长停顿营造终结感\", \"interval_silence\": 500}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 750, \"duration_reason\": \"42字中等长度文本，750 tokens匹配自然语速\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 65, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
INSERT INTO `sub_story_slice` VALUES (195, 6, '{\"text\": \"The three of them were happy.\", \"emo_control\": {\"emo_alpha\": 0.75, \"emo_vector\": [0.3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0], \"emo_vector_reason\": \"明确表达\'高兴\'，调整维度0为0.3\"}, \"slice_reason\": \"句号结尾且情感一致（高兴），语义完整\", \"pause_settings\": {\"pause_reason\": \"积极结局，中等停顿强调喜悦\", \"interval_silence\": 400}, \"duration_control\": {\"max_mel_tokens\": 500, \"duration_reason\": \"8字极短文本，500 tokens避免语速过快\", \"duration_control\": true}}', 66, '2025-10-28 11:44:47', '2025-10-28 11:44:47', b'0');
